from your own writing.

54:52.722 --> 54:55.657
"I promise you
that I will come back and get you.

54:55.759 --> 54:59.058
"I know things are very hard sometimes
in our family.

54:59.162 --> 55:01.494
"I need to go away for a little while
on a writing sabbatical."

55:01.598 --> 55:03.190
